Package storm2013.commands.LEDcommands

Class Summary
Color Color enumeration for the LED strip.
Flash Flash through a series of colors
FlashOnAndOff Flash one color on and off (or solid on if period == 0).
SetColor Sets LED color, then leaves it that way until interrupted somehow.
SetModeFiring Sets LED color for firing.
SetModeMoving Turns lights between white and off, in a sinusoid, with frequency proportional to speed.
SetModeRainbowDanceParty Flashes a bunch of colors very quickly.
SetModeSpinningUp Flashes the LEDs, getting faster as the wheel approaches the target speed.
Spaz Sets the LEDStrip color to some random color 20 times a second, or at some other specified rate.
TurnOff Turn the LEDs off.
